title: Highest CP Pokemon?
body:
Started Pokemon Go yesterday. Shit's going pretty good already level 5 and got some ok pokemons. Finna smash up a gym tomorrow finally join the one true gang team Valor. Living in suburban/rural areas is a fuckin death sentence tho for real no pokestops or gyms close to home, and my neighbourhood literally only has fuckin ratatas. my highest cp is like 73 i think. but im workin on it.

Anyways how yall doin? what level and pokemans you gots?
